<p>You clearly said how important and amazing Cook&#8217;s COO work is and I doubt you&#8217;d ever say anything is &#8220;just implementation.&#8221;  Just want to clarify that if anyone&#8217;s out there writing off what Cook does as &#8220;mere&#8221; execution it ain&#8217;t you.</p>

